Act as a storyboard artist.

Break the following CEFR story into video scenes.

For each scene provide:

1. Scene number
2. Duration
3. Narration text
4. Subtitle text
5. Detailed image generation prompt
6. Camera movement
7. Transition

Requirements:
- Maintain character consistency
- Modern educational illustration with storybook warmth
- Adult-friendly language learning style
- 16:9 landscape
- No text in image
- Visually engaging
- Suitable for AI image generation
- Output as JSON

Story:
Ethan had been looking for a job for three months. To reduce stress, he joined a free wellness group at the local community center. There, he met Leo, a quiet man whom most people avoided. Rumors said Leo was rude and difficult.
One evening, Ethan found his backpack open after a yoga session. His notebook, which contained interview notes, was missing.
“I saw Leo near your bag,” someone whispered.
The next day, Ethan confronted him.
“Did you take my notebook?” Ethan asked.
Leo looked surprised. “No. Why would I do that?”
“You were the last person near my backpack.”
Leo’s face hardened. “People always blame me.”
The conversation ended badly.
Two days later, Ethan received a call for an important interview. When he arrived at the company, the receptionist handed him a notebook.
“A man left this for you yesterday,” she said.
It was his.
Inside was a note: *You dropped this outside the center. Good luck. — Leo*
Embarrassed, Ethan went to find him.
“I’m sorry,” Ethan said.
Leo smiled slightly. “It’s okay. I’m used to surprises. But this time, I guess you were the surprised one.”
The two men laughed, and their conflict finally ended.







## Scene 1 Prompt

Create a 16:9 landscape still image.

Modern educational illustration with storybook warmth. Adult-friendly language-learning style. Clean outlines, expressive facial features, readable body language, bright but natural colors, simple uncluttered background, high visual clarity, professional digital illustration, cinematic composition. No text, no captions, no watermarks.

Ethan is a man in his early 30s with short brown hair, light stubble, and an average build. He wears a blue casual jacket over a light gray shirt and dark jeans.

Show Ethan sitting alone at a small desk in a modest apartment, looking at job applications on a laptop. Several resumes and notes are neatly arranged nearby. Soft morning sunlight comes through a window. Ethan looks tired but determined after three months of searching for work.

